{"title":"【风花食事】豆花*苞谷粑","slug":"rjyh","date":"2022-11-04T14:59:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-18T05:54:35.235Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/rjyh.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"        cook    <br><br> For人间烟火","covers":["https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202106/22/190955y0qqf61kk0h4k978.png","https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202106/22/185643iwrzczr8dkhhkcye.jpg","https://bdn.135editor.com/files/images/editor_styles/8009f60f754f96b178092864c46849f1.jpg"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"ie=edge\">\n  <title>cook</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <br><br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<section style=\"width:630px;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"padding:5px;padding-top:2em;color: #ffA03B;\">\n<section style=\"margin-bottom:-4.0em;margin-left: -6px;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\">\n<section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\">\n<section style=\"border-top-left-radius:10px; display: inline-block;background:#4D8A04;height: 30px;padding: 0px 0.5em 0px 1em;letter-spacing: 2.5px;line-height: 30px;\">\n <b><font color=\"White\"><font size=\"3\">For人间烟火</font></font></b>\n</section>\n<span id=\"more\"></span> \n<section class=\"assistant\" style=\"width:0px; height:0px; border-top:solid 30px transparent; border-left:solid 20px #4D8A04;\"></section>\n<section class=\"assistant\" style=\"width:0px; height:0px; border-top:solid 30px #4D8A04; border-right:solid 20px transparent;margin-left: -20px;\"></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"box-shadow: #BCC1BC 0px 0px 12px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 12px; box-sizing: border-dashed;\">\n<section style=\"border:5px dashed ; solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: #4D8A04; border-radius: 12px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<br><br><br><br>\n<section section style=\"text-align:center; line-height: 3em;\">\n<span style=\"color: #3A661A; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 20px;\">\n<b>一方食事</b>\n</span></section>\n<section section style=\"text-align:center; line-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"color: #285E01; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 13px;\">\nwritten by 风花\n</span></section>\n<br>\n<section style=\"text-align:left; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 200px;\">\n<span style=\"color: #285E01; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 15px;\">\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n一、胆水豆花 ：\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n<br>\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n耗时1个半小时左右\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n黄豆440g+花生60g  需水10斤(6大碗，9分满)\n<!--more-->\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n胆水10g  :水80g\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n泡的水:5斤，时间4小时至8小时\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n果汁机打3次以上。过滤，沸三次\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n80～90度，下配好比例的胆水\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n勺子乘入锅底顺时针缓慢搅动，现絮状\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n盖好锅盖，开微火，随时观察有无清水出现,\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n匀入未清澈处\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n基本清澈，压紧，切好。\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n放盐，烧开，要开时小火，过心，完工\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n<br>\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n二、红糖苞谷粑 ：\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n<br>\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n5斤玉米\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n大概10斤不老不嫩的玉米棒\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n2.5斤肥猪肉\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n可少二三两\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n红糖1斤半\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n可少一二两\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n酵母七八克\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n发酵到蜂窝状\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n包谷叶子，洗净滴干，开工。\n<section style=\"width:80%; border-top:dashed 1px #4D8A04;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"></section>\n</span></section>\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n<div style=\"margin:0px auto;\">\n    <audio style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\" src=\"https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1431915722.mp3\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" loop=\"loop\" controls=\"controls\" type=\"audio/mpeg\"></audio>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section style=\"width: 40px; margin-top: 5px; height: 10px; overflow: hidden;\"></section>\n<p style=\"width:80%; margin-right: 82px; margin-left: 45px;text-align:right;\">\n<img  width=\"100\" _height=\"0\" src=\"https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202106/22/190955y0qqf61kk0h4k978.png\" />\n<br><br><br>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin:-350px;\">\n<section style=\"flex: 1;\">\n<section style=\"width: 200px;background: #ffffff;padding: 10px;margin-left: -520px;transform: rotate(-12.8deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(-12.8deg);-moz-transform: rotate(-12.8deg);-o-transform: rotate(-12.8deg);box-shadow: #BCC1BC  0px 0px 8px;\">\n<img style=\"display: block;width: 100%;\" src=\"https://img.wyc520.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/202106/22/185643iwrzczr8dkhhkcye.jpg\" />\n<section style=\"width: 40px;margin-top: 5px;height: 10px;\">\n<img style=\"display: block;width: 100%;\" src=\"https://bdn.135editor.com/files/images/editor_styles/8009f60f754f96b178092864c46849f1.jpg\" />\n</section>\n</section>\n  </section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</div>\n<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>\n</div>\n<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>\n  </body>\n  </html>","categories":[{"name":"食事","slug":"食事","count":1,"path":"api/categories/食事.json"}],"tags":[]}